{
  "comment_text": {
    "sn1.52:2.2": "The previous discourse had <i lang='pi' translate='no'>patiṭṭhitā</i> (“grounded”, i.e. based on reason), whereas here we have <i lang='pi' translate='no'>adhiṭṭhitā</i> (“committed”, i.e. unwavering). "
  },
